  "body": "Cloud provider volume has a function DiskIsAttached to check whether the volume is still attached to the instance. If the instance is no longer exist (deleted by cloud provider), we can safely assume that the volume is no longer attached to the instance and return false without error for DiskIsAttached(). Currently GCE PD and AWS has the correct behavior, but all other volume plugins do not.  ",
